{"title":"Proust e as artes","markdown":{"headingText":"Proust e as artes","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## As obras em *No Caminho de Swann*\n\nAs obras abaixo são mencionadas por Marcel Proust.\n\n<div class=\"gallery\">\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/1a-o-milagre-de-teofilo-detalhe-da-fachada-de-notre-dame-de-paris.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/1a-o-milagre-de-teofilo-detalhe-da-fachada-de-notre-dame-de-paris.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nO milagre de Teófilo\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/2-relevo-em-pedra-quatro-filhos-de-aymon.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/2-relevo-em-pedra-quatro-filhos-de-aymon.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nPlaca dos Quatro filhos de Aymon\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/4-a-catedral-de-chartres-corot.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/4-a-catedral-de-chartres-corot.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nA Catedral de Chartres\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nJean-Baptiste Camille Corot\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/5-interior-de-parque.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/5-interior-de-parque.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nA Fonte\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nHubert Robert\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/6-vesuvio-em-erupcao.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/6-vesuvio-em-erupcao.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nVesúvio em erupção\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nJoseph Mallord William Turner\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/7-a-ultima-ceia-morghen.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/7-a-ultima-ceia-morghen.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nA Última Ceia\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nRaphael Morghen\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/8-ruinas-a-beira-de-um-lago.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/8-ruinas-a-beira-de-um-lago.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nRuínas à beira de um lago\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nLucas van Uden\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/10-tarot-grigonneur-allegorie-du-monde.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/10-tarot-grigonneur-allegorie-du-monde.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nTarot Carlos VI ou Grigonneur\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/11-coroacao-de-ester.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/11-coroacao-de-ester.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nTapeçaria da Coroação de Ester\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/12-missa-de-santo-eloi.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/12-missa-de-santo-eloi.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nA Missa de Santo Elói\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/13-basilica-saint-denis-tumulos.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/13-basilica-saint-denis-tumulos.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nTúmulo de Luís III e Carlos II\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/14-piazza-del-popolo.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/14-piazza-del-popolo.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nVista da Piazza del Popolo\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nGiovanni Battista Piranesi\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/15-amiens-quatrefeuilles.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/15-amiens-quatrefeuilles.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nAmiens – Quatrefeuilles de la façade\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nEscultores da Catedral de Amiens\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/16-caridade.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/16-caridade.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nCaridade\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nGiotto\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/17-inveja.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/17-inveja.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nInveja\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nGiotto\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/18-justiça.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/18-justiça.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nJustiça\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nAutor: Giotto\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/19-o-sultao-maome-ii.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/19-o-sultao-maome-ii.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nO Sultão Maomé II\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nAutor: Gentile Bellini\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/20a-reis-e-rainhas-do-portico-real-de-chartres.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/20a-reis-e-rainhas-do-portico-real-de-chartres.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nReis e Rainhas de Chartres\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/21-a-entrada-do-delfim-em-paris.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/21-a-entrada-do-delfim-em-paris.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nA entrado do Delfim em Paris\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nAutor: Jean-Auguste Dominique Ingres\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/22-rosacea-norte-notre-dame-de-chartres.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/22-rosacea-norte-notre-dame-de-chartres.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nVitrais da Catedral de Chartres\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/23-aquarela-rei-carlos-iii-de-navarra.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/23-aquarela-rei-carlos-iii-de-navarra.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nRei Carlos II de Navarra\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/24-o-mausoleu-de-Jean-Jacques-Rousseau.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/24-o-mausoleu-de-Jean-Jacques-Rousseau.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nO Mausoléu de Jean-Jacques Rousseau\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nAutor: Hubert Robert\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/25-espinheiros-da-catedral-de-bourges-portal-oeste-do-juizo-final.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/25-espinheiros-da-catedral-de-bourges-portal-oeste-do-juizo-final.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nEspinheiros da Catedral de Bourges\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/26a-igreja-de-saint-loup-de-naud.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/26a-igreja-de-saint-loup-de-naud.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nIgreja Saint-Loup\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/27-ilusoes-perdidas.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/27-ilusoes-perdidas.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nIlusões Perdidas\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nAutor: Charles Gleyre\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/28-procissao-na-praça-de-sao-marcos.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/28-procissao-na-praça-de-sao-marcos.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nProcissão na Praça de São Marcos\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nAutor: Gentile Bellini\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/32a-batismo-dos-selenitas.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/32a-batismo-dos-selenitas.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nO Batismo dos Selenitas\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nVittore Carpaccio\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<a href=\"pagina-obra/33-vista-de-delft.html\">\n<img src=\"imagens/33-vista-de-delft.jpg\">\n</a>\n\n<div class=\"title\">\nVista de Delft\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"artist\">\nJohannes Vermeer\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-